import React from 'react';
import { Box, Typography, Button, Container } from '@mui/material';
import { Link } from 'react-scroll';

const Hero = () => {
  return (
    <Box
      id="hero"
      sx={{
        minHeight: '100vh',
        display: 'flex',
        alignItems: 'center',
        pt: 8,
      }}
    >
      <Container>
        <Typography
          variant="h6"
          color="primary"
          sx={{ mb: 2 }}
        >
          Hello, I'm
        </Typography>
        <Typography
          variant="h1"
          sx={{
            mb: 2,
            fontWeight: 'bold',
            color: 'text.primary',
          }}
        >
          [Your Name]
        </Typography>
        <Typography
          variant="h2"
          sx={{
            mb: 4,
            color: 'text.secondary',
          }}
        >
          Software Developer - Engineer
        </Typography>
        <Box sx={{ mt: 4 }}>
          <Button
            variant="outlined"
            color="primary"
            size="large"
            sx={{ mr: 2 }}
            component="a"
            href="/resume.pdf"
            target="_blank"
          >
            Download CV
          </Button>
          <Button
            variant="contained"
            color="primary"
            size="large"
            component={Link}
            to="contact"
            smooth={true}
            duration={500}
          >
            Contact Info
          </Button>
        </Box>
        <Box sx={{ mt: 4 }}>
          <Button
            component="a"
            href="https://linkedin.com/in/your-profile"
            target="_blank"
            sx={{ mr: 2 }}
          >
            My LinkedIn profile
          </Button>
          <Button
            component="a"
            href="https://github.com/your-username"
            target="_blank"
          >
            My Github profile
          </Button>
        </Box>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Hero;
